node.text: Cali K9 Dog training is more than just obedience. It’s socialization behavior modification, agility and problem-solving technique. At the end of every class I always go through and questions and answers so I can walk people through common issues that are usually easily fixed through the Cali K9 training system, sometimes they just need to hear it from me. Just another fun Saturday doing what I love! 💙🐶#calik9 #dogtraining #Problemsolving

node.text: I am posting this video to show the development of my dog as he prepares to get ready for next year’s trials. These are the beginning phases of tracking and I admit I have been slacking on this portion of the sport but through consistency and repetition I will be where I need to be once competition season starts. I honestly love this dog and feel like he has super high potential to go far so it’s up to me to get off my lazy ass and maximize potential!! Let’s get it! 💪💪💪#calik9 #ipg #dogsport

node.title: Slash’s first time tracking for IGP Dog Sport.

May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Global Strays Invites You Our 3rd Annual Benefit REDEFINING ANIMAL WELFARE GLOBAL STRAYS Hosted by Global Strays President, Elizabeth Shafiroff With Animal Champion Jas Leverette & Georgina Bloomberg Thursday, Sept. 2, 2021 @ 6-9 pm EST ΝΑΙΑ Southampton, NY NAIA HAMPTONS Tito's. https:// Handmade VODKA Tickets third annual- benefit/'.

node.text:
I am so excited to be a special guest at Global Strays’ 3rd Annual Benefit this September! @globalstrays is a non-profit organization dedicated to rescuing strays, supporting shelters, and redefining animal welfare in underserved communities. As a member of their Advisory Council, I want to share this opportunity with you, my fellow dog lovers, to learn more about Global Strays’ work while enjoying an awesome evening of cocktails (open bar), a curated silent auction, hors d'oeuvres, DJ and more! Head over to @globalstrays to purchase tickets or https://www.globalstrays.org/third-annual-benefit/. See you there! 💙🐶🌎⁣ #calik9 #rescue #globalstray #fundraiser 
⁣
#GlobalStrays #OneHealth #RedefiningAnimalWelfare #RescueDog #AnimalWelfare #CharityEventHamptons #DogLover #EducateEngageEmpower
